{"type":"text","text":"{
  "name": "Eiffel Tower",
  "formatted_address": "Av. Gustave Eiffel, 75007 Paris, France",
  "location": {
    "lat": 48.85837009999999,
    "lng": 2.2944813
  },
  "website": "https://www.toureiffel.paris/fr",
  "rating": 4.7,
  "reviews": [
    {
      "author_name": "Els Westhovens",
      "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117423833724294088087/reviews",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "en",
      "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUPuty6r3wzxjdyphKsY63WMPPP-ghPhzKRMQcRUfge0DzxMp4KsQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5",
      "rating": 5,
      "relative_time_description": "2 weeks ago",
      "text": "The Eiffel Tower is truly iconic – a symbol of Paris that’s just as beautiful in person as it is in photos. Whether you're viewing it from the nearby gardens or enjoying it from underneath, it’s an unforgettable sight.\n\nThe area around the tower is lively and full of great spots to take pictures.\n\nEven without going up, just being near the Eiffel Tower is an experience in itself.\nIt is so impressive.\nDefinitely worth a visit if you're in Paris!",
      "time": 1757106473,
      "translated": false
    },
    {
      "author_name": "Gopala krishnan Vellingiri (VGK)",
      "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103007255366888207083/reviews",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "en",
      "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLOP4ak6JIsKPMslcmOOWNP1cNx2wUXRJkE_zum3iY3kUL2=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3",
      "rating": 5,
      "relative_time_description": "in the last week",
      "text": "Visiting the Eiffel Tower for the first time was truly one of the most magical moments of my life. Standing before this iconic structure, I felt an overwhelming sense of joy and excitement. At night, when the tower sparkles, it’s simply breathtaking—an elegant masterpiece glowing against the Paris sky.\n\nThe atmosphere around the Eiffel Tower is filled with energy, with tourists from all over the world gathering to admire its beauty. What makes it even more special is that you can view it from different spots in the city, and each view feels unique.\n\nGoing up to the summit was an unforgettable experience—the panoramic view of Paris from the top left me speechless. Seeing the city’s lights stretch endlessly was both romantic and deeply emotional, making me feel grateful and so alive in that moment.\n\nThe Eiffel Tower is not just a structure; it’s a symbol of love, elegance, and brilliance. My heart was filled with happiness during my visit, and the memory will stay with me forever. ❤️",
      "time": 1758038724,
      "translated": false
    },
    {
      "author_name": "Frank Adrian Martinez Asilda",
      "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108576015254399076123/reviews",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "en",
      "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXi7WVuyGF2VkZFZTo_e9ZQzkL7oTsIzvobSuTSSl6-tCisecD0=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4",
      "rating": 5,
      "relative_time_description": "a month ago",
      "text": "Amazing experience visiting the Tower! We explored all levels with a fantastic guided tour that brought the history to life. The views were breathtaking, and every level had something unique to offer. The guide was informative and engaging, making the visit even more memorable. Everything was well organized and smooth from start to finish. Highly recommend for anyone visiting the region!",
      "time": 1754444107,
      "translated": false
    },
    {
      "author_name": "J Youde",
      "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110888392815502405098/reviews",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "en",
      "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIvu1sYixgQg6v56ggvodjgW3nCzFb7y5b0W880piNPDd8YrA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4",
      "rating": 5,
      "relative_time_description": "in the last week",
      "text": "Absolutely fantastic experience visiting this place. We experienced it first by walking along the Seine River where the views were amazing. We decided to go to the very top off the Eiffel Tower after dusk, when the Tower was lit up, in all its glory and to experience the sparkling of the lights. Also we wanted to see all of Paris lit up from the very top - which was such a magnificent experience. The whole Eiffel Tower evening experience was awesome and it was the highlight of our time in Paris.",
      "time": 1758032096,
      "translated": false
    },
    {
      "author_name": "Kareem A",
      "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104245703854526142031/reviews",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "en",
      "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUp29nqjyEGa9bDqwvXg047ApUn6ngk_M-eG4SgJDJHYNdCS3g=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4",
      "rating": 5,
      "relative_time_description": "2 weeks ago",
      "text": "5/5 ⭐ – Eiffel Tower\nAn absolute must-see in Paris and even more impressive in person than in photos. The structure is massive, with incredible views from every level. Going up at sunset is highly recommended as you can watch the city light up while still seeing it in daylight. The tower sparkles every hour at night, which is a highlight of the visit and creates a great atmosphere along the Seine. Security and entry lines are well-organized, though still busy, so booking tickets in advance saves time. The surrounding Champ de Mars park is clean, spacious, and perfect for photos or a picnic. A world-class landmark that fully lives up to its reputation.",
      "time": 1757097257,
      "translated": false
    }
  ],
