  "rating": 4.7,
  "reviews": [
    {
      "author_name": "Brett Vaughan",
      "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113176475614744790651/reviews",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "en",
      "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKHO4s8CRiPXN1zyC_BvykPTNxSM4MTw3EAvqHaqyjao1KFCQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6",
      "rating": 5,
      "relative_time_description": "2 weeks ago",
      "text": "A beautiful Paris landmark that you have seen in countless TV shows and films. I highly recommend you take the time to venture through one of the tunnels and purchase a ticket to climb the 284 stairs to the top. The views are amazing",
      "time": 1757146134,
      "translated": false
    },
    {
      "author_name": "David Stejkowski",
      "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/116824569077217929560/reviews",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "en",
      "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXRNgz_8-XpRf4MGgpe7nogY2tgRGChiTOj-E6Cz1hJ19gOlMAI=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba7",
      "rating": 5,
      "relative_time_description": "2 weeks ago",
      "text": "What else can be said that hasn’t been already? At the top of the Champs-Élysées, it can be a beautiful experience if you’re looking at it, and a frightening experience if you’re driving around it.  I’ve done both and lived to tell. Even my family was impressed that I was able to navigate the roundabout without any major difficulty.  The view from the top is spectacular.",
      "time": 1757044356,
      "translated": false
    },
    {
      "author_name": "P R",
      "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103228101338139874668/reviews",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "en",
      "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIb3pu4gLuhC5ojyQ3vAM-bc5BySBWR7Bb27c2Fddv7-rrYnA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6",
      "rating": 5,
      "relative_time_description": "a month ago",
      "text": "Magnificent arc located on a busy roundabout.\n\nYou need to take the subway to reach under the arc.\n\nStunning monument. Amazing detailing. Didn't go inside but really loved visiting this historical monument. There was a sombre mood there but very pleasant experience.\n\nWasn't very busy when we visited.\n\nMust visit on a trip to Paris.",
      "time": 1753597992,
      "translated": false
    },
    {
      "author_name": "Irene Greens",
      "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105053630455006477345/reviews",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "en",
      "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXNRAkTS_xn7lAKGl2xwUGOMM0LcY9VmB_IuLwDlyn-Q3B-jLFUqg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5",
      "rating": 4,
      "relative_time_description": "in the last week",
      "text": "Of course, it’s worth visiting if you’re in Paris for the first time – the view from the top is really impressive. Luckily, you don’t have to wait too long to go up. However, the area around is extremely crowded with tourists, people crossing the streets everywhere, so you need to be careful. Also, watch out for pickpockets. Still, as a landmark, it’s definitely beautiful and iconic.",
      "time": 1757865320,
      "translated": false
    },
    {
      "author_name": "Steve Kennedy",
      "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102017015355048931276/reviews",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "en",
      "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVii0mqrg5iEjr1D_UJ8iDjoW2zKmzBhlDIGmbiEKYYNW5A6Zca=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5",
      "rating": 5,
      "relative_time_description": "a week ago",
      "text": "Very cool mount to history. This may not be a great stop if you have children as there is very little interactivity. It is also very difficult for anybody who has mobility impaired as it is 287 steps to this top. There is an elevator, but it takes a special pass and medical information to get access to the elevator.",
