    {
      "author_name": "Chiara Riccioni",
      "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108682707256816699312/reviews",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "en",
      "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIgyk8UEWD_spyaL6mDtU_AhCQohVdoszwiKzJtUhzmwXQMcEk=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3",
      "rating": 5,
      "relative_time_description": "3 weeks ago",
      "text": "very beautiful. quite small in comparison to the others in the city bit there is a lot of beautiful art. there is famous painters but  also minor ones.\nthe collection of Monet's Nympheas is fantastic, suggestive, and very unique.\nits not expensive at all and you dont have to wait much to enter. really recommended",
